data.description: WELCOME HOME!!!! This 1st floor ranch style condo is a 1 Bed 1 Bath plus a Den in the highly desirable Bristol Bay subdivision. The large kitchen offers tile backsplash, Newer Microwave(2022), Refrigerator(2021) and plenty of cabinet space. The Primary bedroom includes plush carpeting and a large walk in closet. Additional features include In-Unit Laundry(2023), detached garage and 1 additional assigned parking space. Plus Bristol Bay is popular clubhouse community that features an outdoor pool, exercise room, sports courts, party room, biking and walking trails. Close to I-88, restaurants and shopping.
